cert.pem and key.pem were generated using (adapted from net/http/internal):

% cd src/crypto/tls # in go source tree
% go run generate_cert.go \
    --rsa-bits 1024 \
    --host 127.0.0.1,::1,littleroot.org,birthdays.littleroot.org,passwords.littleroot.org \
    --ca \
    --start-date "Jan 1 00:00:00 1970" \
    --duration=1000000h
